{"tid":781310,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"深夜好肚餓呀 !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2018-08-15T20:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T21:12:36.000Z","uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"91aefa272b74fc36eb759d52f94fd874fafa4857","tid":781310,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T20:52:22.000Z","msg":"屋企一包餅乾都冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早排親戚送嘅三文魚咁啱食晒 (屌之前仲要叫老豆唔使留比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n得卽食麵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但煮麵又要等 又唔撚想洗煲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好彩喺雪櫃搵到排朱古力頂下肚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以大家有冇咩深宵乾糧推介 等以後唔使餓住肚瞓 做隻飽鬼長赴夢鄉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93325aa670a60a7a0a820b8a6792e6d60d21e5d4","tid":781310,"uid":196013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T20:59:58.000Z","msg":"即食麵當媽咪麵咁食"},{"pid":"846ac1c2a00097dbfe668752d0b3d8d187c5e78e","tid":781310,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T21:06:52.000Z","msg":"唔食嘢"},{"pid":"cfbb41551c68f1765007e65686f353f10a8a45d7","tid":781310,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93325aa670a60a7a0a820b8a6792e6d60d21e5d4","tid":781310,"uid":196013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T20:59:58.000Z","msg":"即食麵當媽咪麵咁食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T21:08:14.000Z","msg":"諗得過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我怕啲粉會太鹹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 上網見過有人將卽食麵包裝當煲用 唔知係咪全部麵都得 ?? ???<br />\n係嘅話就唔使次次都洗個煲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3212c0310f45baa818f5261b99fc298996642fbb","tid":781310,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dis